category.name: TC XML Import Export.Import
category.category_description: Preferences that control import of data in TC XML.

preference.name: PSOcc_custom_attrs_list
preference.preference_description: Updates the custom attributes during the import of data in the TC XML format. A valid value is a comma-separated list of the custom attributes defined on the PSOccurrence (e.g. "ATTR1,ATTR2,ATTR3").
